an language|Italian]]\n| {{flag|Italy}}<br>{{RSM}}<br>{{flag|Switzerland}}<br>{{flag|Vatican City}}\n| [[Accademia della Crusca]] (''Academy of the bran'')\n|-\n| [[Japanese language|Japanese]]\n| {{flag|Japan}}\n| No official centralized regulation, but ''de facto'' regulations by [[Agency for Cultural Affairs]] (\u6587\u5316\u5e81) at the [[Ministry of Education, Culture, Sports, Science and Technology (Japan)|Ministry of Education of Japan]] (\u6587\u90e8\u79d1\u5b66\u7701)\n|-\n| [[Kannada]]\n| {{flagicon|India}} [[Karnataka]]\n| Various academies and Government of [[Karnataka]]\n|-\n| [[Kashubian language|Kashubian]]\n| {{flag|Poland}}\n| Commission of the Kashubian Language [https://web.archive.org/web/20071218233200/http://www.kaszubi.pl/o/rjk/?p=page&page_id=462]\n|-\n| [[Kazakh language|Kazakh]]\n| {{flag|Kazakhstan}}\n| [https://web.archive.org/web/20111102035137/http://www.mk.gov.kz/ Ministry of Culture of Kazakhstan]\n|-\n| [[Khmer language|Khmer]]\n| {{flag|Cambodia}}\n| [[Royal Academy of Cambodia]] (\u179a\u17b6\u1787\u1794\u178e\u17d2\u178c\u17b7\u178f\u17d2\u1799\u179f\u1797\u17b6\u1780\u1798\u17d2\u1796\u17bb\u1787\u17b6)\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" | [[Korean language|Korean]]\n| {{flag|South Korea}}\n| [[National Institute of the Korean Language]] (\uad6d\ub9bd\uad6d\uc5b4\uc6d0/\u570b\u7acb\u570b\u8a9e\u9662)\n|-\n| {{flag|North Korea}}\n| The Language Research Institute, Academy of Social Science (\uc0ac\ud68c\uacfc\ud559\uc6d0 \uc5b4\ud559\uc5f0\uad6c\uc18c/\u793e\u6703\u79d1\u5b78\u9662 \u8a9e\u5b78\u7814\u7a76\u6240)\n|-\n| {{flag|China}}\n| China Korean Language Regulatory Commission (\uc911\uad6d\uc870\uc120\uc5b4\uaddc\ubc94\uc704\uc6d0\ud68c/\u4e2d\u56fd\u671d\u9c9c\u8bed\u89c4\u8303\u59d4\u5458\u4f1a)\n|-\n| [[Kven language|Kven]]\n| {{flag|Norway}}\n| [[Kainun institutti]]&nbsp;\u2013 kvensk institutt\n|-\n| [[Kurdish language|Kurdish]]\n| {{flag|Kurdistan}}\n| [[Kurdish Academy]]&nbsp;\u2013 \u0626\u06d5\u06a9\u0627\u062f\u06cc\u0645\u06cc\u