gal]]\n| [[Paschimbanga Bangla Akademi]] (\u09aa\u09b6\u09cd\u099a\u09bf\u09ae\u09ac\u0999\u09cd\u0997 \u09ac\u09be\u0982\u09b2\u09be \u0986\u0995\u09be\u09a6\u09c7\u09ae\u09bf)\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" | [[Berber languages|Berber]]\n| {{flag|Morocco}}\n| [[Royal Institute of the Amazigh Culture|Royal Institute of Amazight Culture]]\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | {{flag|Algeria}}\n| [[Haut-Conseil \u00e0 l'amazighit\u00e9]]\n|-\n|[[Algerian Academy of Amazigh Language]]\n|-\n| [[Central Bikol language|Central Bikol]]\n| {{flag|Philippines}}\n| [[:bcl:Academia Bicolana|Academia Bicolana]] ''defunct''\n|-\n| [[Bosnian language|Bosnian]]\n| {{flag|Bosnia and Herzegovina}}<br>{{flagicon image|Bosniak National Flag in Sandzak.svg}} [[Sand\u017eak]]\n| [[University of Sarajevo]]\n|-\n| [[Bulgarian language|Bulgarian]]\n| {{flag|Bulgaria}}\n| [[Institute for Bulgarian Language]] at the [[Bulgarian Academy of Sciences]]\n|-\n| [[Burmese language|Burmese]]\n| {{flag|Myanmar}}\n| [[Myanmar Language Commission]]\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | [[Catalan language|Catalan]]\n| {{flag|Catalonia}}\n| [[Institute of Catalan Studies]] (''Institut d'Estudis Catalans'')\n|-\n| {{flag|Valencian Community}}\n| [[Acad\u00e8mia Valenciana de la Llengua]] (for the [[Valencian]] standard)\n|-\n| [[Cebuano language|Cebuano]]\n| {{flag|Philippines}}\n| [[Visayan Academy of Arts and Letters]] (''Akademyang Bisaya'')\n|-\n| [[Cherokee language|Cherokee]]\n| {{flag|Cherokee Nation}}\n| Council of the Cherokee Nation (\u13e3\u13b3\u13a9\u13af \u13a0\u13f0\u13b5)<ref>[https://cherokee.legistar.com/LegislationDetail.aspx?ID=266941&GUID=C8EC5F0A-E523-49A0-92BD-42041FCE32EAl Council of the Cherokee Nation]</ref>\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\" | [[Standard Chinese]]\n| {{flag|China}}\n| [[State Language Work Committee]] (\u56fd\u5bb6\u8bed\u8a00\u6587\u5b57\u5de5\u4f5c\u59d4\u5458\u4f1a)\n|-\n| {{flag|Republic of China}}\n| [[National Languages Committee]] (\u570b\u8a9e\u63a8\u884c\u59d4\u54e1\u6703)\n|-\n| {{flag|Singapore}}\n| [[