ese Language)\n|-\n| [[Mixtecan languages|Mixtec]]\n| {{flag|Mexico}}\n| [[Academy of the Mixtec Language]] (''Ve'e Tu'un S\u00e1vi'')\n|-\n| [[Khalkha Mongolian]]\n| {{flag|Mongolia}}\n| Council of the official state language (\u0422\u04e9\u0440\u0438\u0439\u043d \u0445\u044d\u043b\u043d\u0438\u0439 \u0437\u04e9\u0432\u043b\u04e9\u043b). Decisions have to be confirmed by the Mongolian government.<ref>{{cite web|url=http://legalinfo.mn/law/details/486 |title=\u0425\u0443\u0443\u043b\u0438\u0439\u043d \u043d\u044d\u0433\u0434\u0441\u044d\u043d \u043f\u043e\u0440\u0442\u0430\u043b \u0441\u0430\u0439\u0442 |work=Legalinfo.mn |language=mn |url-status=live |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150914161424/http://legalinfo.mn/law/details/486 |archive-date=14 September 2015 }}</ref>\n|-\n| [[Chakhar Mongolian]]\n| {{flag|China}}\n| Council for Language and Literature Work\n|-\n| [[Nepali language|Nepali]]\n| {{flag|Nepal}}\n| Language Academy of Nepal\n|-\n| [[Norwegian language|Norwegian (Riksm\u00e5l/Bokm\u00e5l)]]\n| rowspan=\"2\" |  {{flag|Norway}}\n| [[Norwegian Academy]]\n|-\n| [[Norwegian language|Norwegian Bokm\u00e5l<br>Norwegian Nynorsk]]\n| [[Norwegian Language Council]]\n|-\n| [[Occitan language|Occitan]]\n| {{flag|Occitania}}<br>{{flag|France}}<br>{{flag|Spain}}<br>{{flag|Monaco}}<br>{{flag|Italy}}\n| Lo Congr\u00e8s Permanent de la lenga occitana (''the permanent congress of occitan language'')<ref>{{cite web |title=Lo Congr\u00e8s |url=http://www.locongres.org |website=locongres.org |accessdate=25 October 2019}}</ref><br>Institut d'Estudis Aranesi ([[Aranese dialect|Aranese]])<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.conselharan.org/reconeishenca-der-institut-destudis-aranesi-coma-academia-e-autoritat-linguistica-der-occitan-aranes-en-aran/|title=Reconeishen\u00e7a der Institut d\u2019Estudis Aranesi coma academia e autoritat ling\u00fcistica der occitan, aran\u00e9s en Aran - Conselh Generau d'Aran|website=conselharan.org}}</ref><br>[[Conselh de la Lenga Occitana]]\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | [[Pashto language|Pashto]]\n| {{flag|Afghanistan}}\n| [[Academy of Sciences of Afghanistan]]\n|-\n| {{flag|Pakistan}}\n| [[Pashto Academy]]\n|-\n| [[Persian language|Persian]]\n| {{flag|Iran}}<br>{{flag|Tajikistan}}<br>{{flag|Afghanistan}}<br>{{flag|Uzbekistan}}\n| [[Academy of Persian Language and Literature]] ({{lang|fa|\u0641\u0631\u0647\u0646\u06af\u0633\u062a\u0627\u0646 \u0632\u0628\u0627\u0646 \u0648 \u0627\u062f\u0628 \u0641\u0627\u0631\u0633\u06cc}})\n|-\n| [[Paiwan language|Paiwan]]\n| {{flag|Republic of China}}\n| [https://www.apc.gov.tw/portal/index.html?lang=en_US Council of Indigenous Peoples]\n|-\n| [[Polish language|Polish]]\n| {{flag|Poland}}\n| [[Polish Language Council]] (''Rada J\u0119zyka Polskiego''), of the [[Polish Academy of Sciences]]\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" | [[Portuguese language|Portuguese]]\n| {{flag|Portugal}}\n| [[Academia das Ci\u00eancias de Lisboa, Classe de Letras]]\n|-\n| {{flag|Brazil}}\n| [[Academia Brasileira de Letras]] (Brazilian Literary Academy)\n|-\n| {{flag|Galicia}}\n| [[Galician Academy of the Portuguese Language]] (Academia Galega da Lingua Portuguesa)\n|-\n| [[Quechua language|Quechua]]\n| {{flag|Peru}}\n| [[Academia Mayor de la Lengua Quechua|High Academy of the Quechua Language]] (''Qheswa simi hamut'ana kuraq suntur'')\n|-\n| [[Rohingya language|Rohingya]]\n| {{flagicon image|Rohingya flag.png}} [[Arakan]] ([[Rakhine State]])\n| [[Rohingya Language Academy]] (\ud803\udd0c\ud803\udd1f\ud803\udd07\ud803\udd25\ud803\udd1d\ud803\udd1a\ud803\udd12\ud803\udd19\ud803\udd1d \ud803\udd0e\ud803\udd1f\ud803\udd01\ud803\udd1d\ud803\udd15 \ud803\udd00\ud803\udd20\ud803\udd11\ud803\udd1d\ud803\udd0b\ud803\udd20\ud803\udd14\ud803\udd1e)\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | [[Romanian language|Romanian]]\n| {{flag|Romania}}\n| Institutul de Lingvistic\u01ce al [[Romanian Academy|Academiei Rom\u00e2ne]] (Institute for Linguistics of the [[Romanian Academy]])\n|-\n| {{flag|Moldova}}\n| [[Academy of Sciences of Moldova|Aca